{"tid":986870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰轉機？中國提出2024貿差減到0 / 傳美國準備立法限制中資電訊商喺美國做生意","createTime":"2019-01-18T23:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T07:45:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1084a84858c66c5dec688b507d89ebbd34fc75d0","tid":986870,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T23:26:44.000Z","msg":"外電突傳中國提出消除美中貿易逆差方法，刺激股市造好，美股漲逾230點，夜期尾市亦升逾220點，報27325點水平。<br />\n<br />\n據彭博引述知情人士表示，中國提議將對美國商品的年進口額合計提高逾1萬億美元，以尋求到2024年將中國對美國的貿易順差，從去年的3,230億美元減少到零。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，中國是在上次北京舉行的會談中，提出了上述建議，但美國談判代表對此持懷疑態度，但同時對中國提出更高要求，希望在未來兩年內解決貿易失衡問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2255549/【中美貿易戰】外電傳中國建議進口萬億美元商品%20夜期漲逾220點?mtc=b0002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2255549%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E5%A4%96%E9%9B%BB%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%2520%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%9F%E6%BC%B2%E9%80%BE220%E9%BB%9E%3Fmtc%3Db0002&d=MrnPEmDsmOOM%2FL8nCE2VhACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=dee366bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2255549/【中美貿易戰】外電傳中國建議進口萬億美元商品%20夜期漲逾220點?mtc=b0002</a><br />\n<br />\nU.S. Preparing Trump Order to Restrict Chinese Telecoms, Sources Say<br />\n<br />\nMargaret Talev<br />\nCommerce Department to have discretion to review products<br />\n<br />\nThe Trump administration is preparing an executive order that could significantly restrict Chinese state-owned telecom companies from operating in the U.S. over national security concerns, according to people familiar with the matter.<br />\n<br />\nThe order, which hasn&rsquo;t yet been presented to the president, would not mention companies such as Huawei Technologies Co. or ZTE Corp. by name and would not outright ban U.S. sales by the firms. But it would give greater authority to the Commerce Department to review products and purchases by companies connected to adversarial countries, including China, one of the people said.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-01-18/u-s-said-to-prepare-trump-order-to-restrict-chinese-telecoms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-01-18%2Fu-s-said-to-prepare-trump-order-to-restrict-chinese-telecoms&d=MrnPEmDsmOOM%2FL8nCE2VhACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4f9eef76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-01-18/u-s-said-to-prepare-trump-order-to-restrict-chinese-telecoms</a>"},{"pid":"e30abccaf0106ae21dfeadf2d7050665287cfc81","tid":986870,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T23:28:30.000Z","msg":"噉睇2月真係會支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ef36ffe687a82cdec2e7d7bccc19d66c4914fb","tid":986870,"uid":6347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T23:40:15.000Z","msg":"傾左咁耐連大方向都未傾成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5802b12cf6b9135c61f9e7f264e9fb66a10885","tid":986870,"uid":66686,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T23:42:00.000Z","msg":"2024<br />\n又想撚狗<br />\n等到trump落台<br />\n信你都on9啦死支狗"},{"pid":"764d206b618fc616f092e77050575b470511a9c4","tid":986870,"uid":2267,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T23:42:41.000Z","msg":"嗱，支那人承諾嘅嘢，如果唔係即刻做，所以嘢都係吹出嚟！<br />\n如果脫現到嘅，我裸跑尖沙咀又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a068358164b25e717463b4b4a12af85ae7f75ff","tid":986870,"uid":136216,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T23:42:47.000Z","msg":"信共產黨一成都是笑話，根本就是拖時間&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pi